vestigating%20the%20matter%2C%20but%20right%20now%2C%20we%20can't%20say%20anything%20definitive%20about%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689750900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fmgfsoqmg_assam-silchar-clash-ndtv_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-locals-hurt-in-clashes-over-assam-19-year-olds-alleged-rape-murder-4221055%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teenager%20had%20been%20reported%20missing%20four%20days%20prior%20and%20her%20mutilated%20body%20was%20found%20in%20an%20under-construction%20building%20in%20the%20Dwarbond%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-locals-hurt-in-clashes-over-assam-19-year-olds-alleged-rape-murder-4221055%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-locals-hurt-in-clashes-over-assam-19-year-olds-alleged-rape-murder-4221055%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-locals-hurt-in-clashes-over-assam-19-year-olds-alleged-rape-murder-4221055%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Story%20Behind%20INDIA%3A%20Who%20Came%20Up%20With%20It%20And%20Alternatives%20Suggested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20two%20days%20of%20discussions%20and%20many%20suggestions%20before%20the%2026-member%20opposition%20front%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20acronym%20for%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20it%20was%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea.%20The%20party%20suggested%20the%20name%20to%20a%20few%20allies%20well%20before%20the%20meeting%2C%20to%20test%20the%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20reportedly%20had%20several%20conversations%20with%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20it%20was%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20who%20proposed%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20alliance.%20After%20the%20name%20was%20suggested%2C%20different%20parties%20floated%20more%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20suggested%20India%20Main%20Alliance%20(IMA)%20or%20India%20Main%20Front%20(IMF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20felt%20INDIA%20sounded%20similar%20to%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20He%20reportedly%20also%20questioned%20how%20INDIA%20could%20be%20the%20name%20of%20a%20political%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20ally%20Viduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%20(VCK)%20suggested%20Save%20India%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20parties%20reportedly%20suggested%20We%20for%20India%20alliance.%20But%20many%20felt%20it%20sounded%20like%20a%20slogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20deliberations%2C%20the%20parties%20agreed%20upon%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20speaking%20last%2C%20had%20emphatically%20pushed%20for%20the%20name%20INDIA%2C%20said%20the%20Congress.%20He%20argued%20that%20the%20opposition%20could%20create%20an%20%26quot%3BINDIA%20vs%20NDA%26quot%3B%20narrative.%20In%20the%20press%20briefing%2C%20he%20even%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BModi%20versus%20I.N.D.I.A%26quot%3B%20battle%20for%20the%202024%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20defending%20the%20Constitution%2C%20voice%20of%20Indians%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%20You%20know%20what%20happens%20to%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20fight%20the%20idea%20of%20India...%20The%20fight%20is%20between%20NDA%20and%20INDIA%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20INDIA%2C%20his%20ideology%20and%20INDIA.%20India%20always%20wins%20all%20fights%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20is%20about%20two%20different%20ideas%20of%20India...%20The%20voice%20of%20the%20country%20is%20being%20stifled.%20The%20fight%20is%20for%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20country.%20So%20this%20name%20was%20chosen%20--%20INDIA%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20Congress%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20was%20originally%20conceived%20as%20the%20Indian%20National%20Democratic%20Inclusive%20Alliance.%20But%20some%20parties%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20had%20a%20similar%20ring%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20some%20leaders%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%26quot%3B%20also%20means%20%26quot%3Binclusive%26quot%3B%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20repetitive.%20Finally%2C%20the%20leaders%20decided%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BD%26quot%3B%20in%20INDIA%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bdevelopmental%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20posts%20from%20different%20leaders%20caused%20a%20confusion%2C%20with%20some%20using%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%26quot%3B%20and%20others%20saying%20%26quot%3Bdevelopmental%26quot%3B%20while%20announcing%20the%20new%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20opposition%20announced%20the%20name%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20suggested%20a%20new%20expansion%20for%20NDA%20-%20%26quot%3BNew%20India%2C%20Developed%20Nation%2C%20Aspiration%20of%20People%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689750780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fval1k918_rahul-gandhi-mamata-banerjee-_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-story-behind-india-who-came-up-with-it-and-alternatives-suggested-4221192%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20took%20two%20days%20of%20discuss