er%20person%20abroad%20were%20part%20of%20a%202017%20murder%20case.%20The%20one%20abroad%20supplied%20them%20with%20weapons%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20activities%2C%20Mr%20Dayanand%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20police%20officer%20added%20that%20the%20Bengaluru%20Police%20is%20coordinating%20with%20central%20agencies%20to%20track%20down%20Junaid.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689749340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ffm4s1t_bengaluru-terrorists_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-suspected-terrorists-arrested-in-bengaluru-for-plotting-attack-cops-4221131%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20suspected%20terrorists%20were%20arrested%20in%20Bengaluru%20today%20by%20the%20Central%20Crime%20Branch%20(CCB)%20for%20allegedly%20planning%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-suspected-terrorists-arrested-in-bengaluru-for-plotting-attack-cops-4221131%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-suspected-terrorists-arrested-in-bengaluru-for-plotting-attack-cops-4221131%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-suspected-terrorists-arrested-in-bengaluru-for-plotting-attack-cops-4221131%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uncertainty%20Over%202026%20Commonwealth%20Games%20After%20Victoria%20Backs%20Out%20as%20Host%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19115011%2FCommonwealth_Games_closing_ceremony_picture.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20state%20of%20Victoria%20in%20Australia%20has%20pulled%20out%20being%20a%20host%20for%20the%202026%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20because%20of%20the%20rising%20expected%20cost%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Victorial%20premier%20Daniel%20Andrews%20said%20that%20while%20initially%202.6%20billion%20Australian%20dollars%20had%20been%20budgeted%20for%20the%20event%2C%20recent%20estimates%20showed%20that%20the%20cost%20had%20gone%20up%20to%20seven%20billion%20Australian%20dollars.%20In%20rupees%2C%20that%20a%20rise%20from%20Rs%2014%2C760%20crore%20to%20Rs%2039%2C360%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20his%20decision%20on%20Twitter%2C%20Andrew%20wrote%20that%20it%20had%20become%20clear%20that%20hosting%20the%20games%20would%20bring%20far%20more%20costs%20than%20benefits%20to%20the%20state.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%2C%20his%20government%20will%20spend%20the%20budgeted%20money%20on%20increasing%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%93%20both%20for%20sports%20and%20otherwise%2C%20through%20facilities%2C%20housing%20projects%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20main%20reason%20we%20agreed%20to%20host%20the%20Games%20was%20to%20create%20a%20big%20lasting%20benefit%20for%20our%20regions%20%E2%80%93%20with%20more%20housing%2C%20boosts%20to%20tourism%20and%20sporting%20infrastructure%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dan%20Andrews%20(%40DanielAndrewsMP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDanielAndrewsMP%2Fstatus%2F1681087785367904256%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20projects%20will%20create%20around%203%2C000%20jobs%20right%20around%20the%20state%2C%20and%20deliver%20what%20our%20regional%20communities%20have%20asked%20for.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Andrews%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commonwealth%20Games%20Federation%20now%20has%20to%20immediately%20search%20for%20a%20new%20host.%20All%20other%20Australian%20states%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F2026-commonwealth-games-victoria-explained-what-next-for-commonwealth-games-after-australia-pulls-out-as-host-4217271%5C%22%3Ehave%20reportedly%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20fill%20in.%20Victoria%E2%80%99s%20decision%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20reason%20behind%20it%20%E2%80%93%20has%20also%20created%20further%20conversations%20on%20whether%20these%20games%2C%20arising%20out%20of%20a%20colonial%20history%2C%20are%20required%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Federation%20said%20it%20is%20working%20to%20locate%20a%20new%20host.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20taking%20advice%20on%20the%20options%20available%20to%20us%20and%20remain%20committed%20to%20finding%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20Games%20in%202026%20that%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20our%20athletes%20and%20the%20wider%20Commonwealth%20Sport%20Movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20consecutive%20time%20that%20there%20has%20been%20controversy%20regarding%20the%20games%E2%80%99%20host.%20In%202022%2C%20Durban%2C%20South%20Africa%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20right%20to%20host%20the%20games%20because%20it%20had%20allegedly%20missed%20deadlines%20and%20failed%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20its%20bid%2C%20and%20Birmingham%20was%20roped%20in%20to%20host%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20uncertainty%20grips%20the%20future%20of%20the%20games%2C%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fmore-sports%2Fothers%2Fahmedabad-may-bid-for-2026-commonwealth-games%2Farticleshow%2F101906322.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20may%20bid%20to%20host%20the%202026%20games%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20report%20quoted