's%20Party%20On%20INDIA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20the%2026%20like-minded%20parties%20for%20not%20inviting%20All-India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20in%20the%20two-day%20opposition%20meeting%20concluded%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20party%20leader%20Waris%20Pathan%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bso%20called%26quot%3B%20secular%20parties%20are%20treating%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20untouchables%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIMIM%20national%20spokesperson%20also%20questioned%20how%20can%20someone%20ignore%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20so%20called%20secular%20parties%20did%20not%20call%20us%2C%20we%20are%20political%20untouchables%20for%20them.%20There%20are%20leaders%20who%20were%20once%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20including%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%20We%20saw%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20abusing%20Congress%20during%20the%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20but%20even%20he%20is%20sitting%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Even%20we%20(AIMIM)%20are%20putting%20efforts%20to%20defeat%20BJP%20in%202024%2C%20but%20they%20(Opposition%20parties)%20are%20ignoring%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20and%20our%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20joint%20meeting%20came%20to%20an%20end%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20the%2026%20parties%20agreeing%20to%20come%20up%20under%20one%20name%20-%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%2C%20or%20INDIA%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20media%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20we%20were%20UPA%20and%20now%20all%20the%2026%20parties%20have%20given%20a%20name%20to%20the%20opposition%20and%20that%20is%20-%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%20Everybody%20has%20agreed%20upon%20this%2C%20and%20the%20resolution%20for%20the%20name%20was%20passed%20unanimously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20came%20as%20top%20leaders%20of%2026%20Opposition%20parties%20from%20across%20the%20country%20met%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20discuss%20a%20united%20strategy%20to%20take%20on%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20alliance%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%20chief%20Thol%20Thirumavalavan%20said%20that%20the%20name%20was%20proposed%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20name%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20-%20INDIA%20was%20proposed%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20After%20a%20long%20discussion%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20be%20called%20as%20'Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20VCK%20chief%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20said%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20justified%20why%20it%20should%20be%20INDIA%20during%20the%20discussion%20in%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20collective%20effort.%20We%20all%20sat%20together%2C%20and%20we%20all%20decided%20on%20names.%20Rahul%20ji%20spearheaded%20this%2C%20he%20justified%20why%20it%20should%20be%20INDIA%20he%20argued%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinate%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20representatives%20of%20the%2026%20parties%20-%2010%20more%20than%20the%2016%20parties%20which%20had%20met%20in%20Patna%20on%20June%2023%20-%20also%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20an%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%2C%20including%20all%20the%20major%20parties%2C%20and%20a%20'secretariat'%20in%20Delhi%20for%20campaign%20management%20and%20for%20coordinating%20the%20working%20of%20various%20sub-committees%2C%20which%20will%20take%20up%20specific%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20opposition%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Mumbai%3B%20the%20date%20will%20be%20announced%20soon.%20An%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%20will%20be%20set%20up.%20Names%20of%20committee%20members%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20called%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20next%20year%20a%20fight%20between%20INDIA%20and%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20fight%20is%20not%20between%202%20political%20formations%20but%20the%20fight%20is%20to%20defend%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%20If%20you%20will%20see%20history%2C%20you%20will%20find%20that%20nobody%20has%20been%20able%20to%20fight%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%20It's%20a%20fight%20between%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20while%20warning%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20centre%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNDA%2C%20BJP%2C%20can%20you%20challenge%20INDIA%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20love%20our%20motherland.%20We%20are%20the%20patriotic%20people%20of%20the%20country.%20We%20are%20for%20the%20country%2C%20the%20world%2C%20farmers%2C%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20--%20Hindus%2C%20Dalits%2C%20minorities%2C%20farmers%2C%20in%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Manipur%20-%20are%20under%20threat%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20whose%20only%20job%20is%20%26quot%3Bbuying%20and%20selling%20governments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20press%20conference%20said%20that%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20like-minded%20parties%20came%20to%20Karnataka's%20Bengaluru%20to%20save%20the%20country%20from%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%209%20years%2C%20PM%20Modi%20could%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20but%20he%20destroyed%20all%20the%20sectors.%20We%20have%20gathered%20here%20not%20for%20ourselves%20but%20to%20save%20the%20country%20from%20hatred...%26quot%3B%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689748680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2F2b9b20cg_asaduddin-owaisi-pti-_625x300_10_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-are-political-untouchables-for-them-a-owaisis-party-on-i-n-d-i-a-4220682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20party%20AIMIM%20has%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%2026%20like-minded%20parties%20for%20not%20inviting%20All-India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20in%20the%20two-day%20opposition%20meeting%20concluded%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-are-political-untouchables-for-them-a-owaisis-party-on-i-n-d-i-a-4220682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-are-political-untouchables-for-them-a-owaisis-party-on-i-n-d-i-a-4220682%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-are-political-untouchables-for-them-a-owaisis-party-on-i-n-d-i-a-4220682%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Video%2C%20Under-20%20Champ%20Questions%20Wrestler%20Vinesh's%20Asian%20Games%20Selection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReigning%20Under-20%20World%20Champion%20Antim%20Panghal%20on%20Wednesday%20questioned%20the%20Asian%20Games%20trials%20exemption%20given%20to%20to%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20asserting%20that%20not%20just%20she%20but%20many%20other%20Indian%20wrestlers%20are%20capable%20of%20beating%20the%20celebrated%20grappler%20in%20the%2053kg%20category.%20Vinesh%20(53kg)%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20(65kg)%20were%2