Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20year%2C%20in%20the%20Junior%20World%20Championships%2C%20I%20had%20won%20a%20gold%20medal%20and%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20wrestler%20from%20India%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat.%20In%20the%202023%20Asian%20Championships%20I%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%2C%20but%20Vinesh%20has%20no%20achievement%20to%20show%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20She%20was%20also%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSakshi%20Malik%20has%20also%20won%20an%20Olympic%20medal%2C%20she%20too%20is%20not%20being%20sent.%20What%20is%20so%20special%20about%20Vinesh%20that%20she%20is%20being%20sent.%20Just%20organise%20trials.%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20that%20I%20am%20the%20only%20one%20who%20can%20beat%20Vinesh.%20There%20are%20several%20other%20girls%20who%20can%20beat%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Panghal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20got%20direct%20entry%20for%20the%20Asian%20Games%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20a%20medal%20winner%20at%20the%20World%20Championship%20last%20year.%20She%20is%20currently%20training%20in%20Budapest%2C%20Hungary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanghal%20alleged%20that%20during%20the%20Birmingham%20Asian%20Games%20trials%20too%2C%20she%20had%20got%20a%20raw%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20CWG%20trials%20were%20taking%20place%2C%20I%20had%20bouts%20against%20her%2C%20then%20too%20they%20(officials)%20cheated%20me.%20I%20said%20koi%20nahin%20(it's%20okay)%2C%20I%20will%20try%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics%20by%20going%20to%20the%20(Hangzhou)%20Asian%20Games.%20But%20now%20they%20are%20saying%20they%20will%20send%20Vinesh.%20This%20is%20not%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20also%20saying%20that%20the%20one%20who%20goes%20for%20the%20Asian%20Games%20will%20also%20go%20for%20the%20World%20Championships.%20And%2C%20the%20one%20who%20wins%20a%20medal%20at%20Worlds%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Olympics%20(in%20Paris).%20We%20have%20also%20been%20training%20hard%20for%20years