%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nigerian%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20team%20experienced%20a%20similar%20issue.%C2%A0The%20Nigerian%20Football%20Federation%20is%20witholding%20match%20bonuses%20for%20its%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20players%20who%C2%A0refused%20to%20train%C2%A0because%20of%20outstanding%20wage%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ET%3C%2Fspan%3Ehe%20dispute%20was%20finally%20resolved%20by%20the%20Motsepe%20Foundation%20%E2%80%93%20a%20charity%20dedicated%20to%20fighting%20for%20diversity%20set%20up%20by%20Confederation%20of%20African%20Football%20(CAF)%20president%20and%20billionaire%20businessman%20Patrice%20Motsepe%20%E2%80%93%20which%20provided%20a%20donation%20for%20the%20players%20to%20share.%20But%20a%20%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ESAFA%20official%20reportedly%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ecalled%20the%20players%20%E2%80%9Cmercenaries%E2%80%9D%C2%A0and%20%E2%80%9Ctraitors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ESouth%20Africa%20and%20Nigeria%20are%3C%2Fspan%3E%20not%20the%20only%20nations%20struggling%20to%20pay%20their%20players.%20A%20recent%20survey%20from%20FIFPRO%20%E2%80%93%20a%20trade%20union%20representing%20international%20professional%20footballers%20%E2%80%93%20showed%20that%2038%25%20of%20CAF%20women%20footballers%20said%20that%20payments%20need%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20improvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20gender%20pay%20gap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%C2%A029%25%20of%20international%20women%20footballers%20said%20that%20they%20had%20not%20received%20any%20payments%20from%20their%20national%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESAFA%20has%20announced%20equal%20pay%20for%20all%20players.%20Zambia%20and%20Sierra%20Leone%20were%20so%20far%20the%20only%20other%20African%20countries%20who%20implemented%20equal%20pay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EBut%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eit%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20find%20exact%20payment%20figures.%20DW%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20national%20football%20federations%20of%20Morocco%2C%20Nigeria%20and%20South%20Africa%20about%20financial%20arrangements%20for%20men%20and%20women%20in%20previous%20World%20Cups%20%E2%80%93%20but%20no%20response%20was%20received%20before%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zambian%C2%A0men%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20never%20played%20in%20a%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20national%20federations%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EFIFA%E2%80%99s%20payments%20are%20clear%3A%20Every%20individual%20competing%20in%20the%20group%20stage%C2%A0will%20earn%20%2430%2C000%20(%E2%82%AC26%2C667)%C2%A0directly%20from%20FIFA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20was%20usually%20transferred%20to%20the%20federations%2C%20resulting%20in%20lower%20individual%20payments%2C%20however%C2%A0it%20is%20a%20huge%20contrast%20to%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20where%C2%A0each%20nation%20received%20%249%20million%20for%20participating%20in%20the%20group%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoor%20working%20conditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EThe%20South%20African%20women%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20team%20boycotted%20a%20warm-up%20because%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20their%20pitch%E2%80%99s%20clay%20and%20grass%20surface%20could%20have%20led%20to%20injuries%20%E2%80%93%20considered%20too%20risky%20so%20close%20to%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EZambia%E2%80%99s%20players%C2%A0also%20experience%3C%2Fspan%3Ed%20poorly-maintained%20pitches.%20Midfielder%20Evarine%20Katongo%20told%20German%20broadcaster%20ntv%20that%20the%20better-quality%20training%20grounds%20are%20reserved%20mainly%20for%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20women%20get%20less%20time%20to%20train%20and%20have%20to%20make%20room%20for%20the%20men%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%C2%A0Katongo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20players%20from%C2%A0Zambia%20and%20South%20Africa%20who%20have%20to%20play%20on%20poor%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIFPRO%E2%80%99s%20report%20shows%20that%C2%A026%25%20of%20CAF%E2%80%99s%C2%A0women%20footballers%20indicated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20improvement%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20improvement%E2%80%9D%20is%20needed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20match%20day%20stadiums%20and%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20quality%20of%20training%20pitches%2C%2020%25%20of%20respondents%C2%A0stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20improvement%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20improvement%E2%80%9D%20was%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ESexual%20abuse%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EA%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0report%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0claimed%20that%20Zambia%E2%80%99s%20head%20coach%2C%20Bruce%20Mwape%2C%20is%20under%20investigation%C2%A0by%20the%20Football%20Association%20of%20Zambia%20(FAZ)%C2%A0which%20has%20since%20been%20referred%20to%20FIFA%20and%20the%20police.%20The%20coach%20is%20accused%20of%20sexual%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20he%20wants%20to%20sleep%20with%20someone%2C%20you%20have%20to%20say%20yes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20normal%20that%20the%20coach%20sleeps%20with%20the%20players%20in%20our%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20unnamed%C2%A0player%20in%20Zambian%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20team%20told%20the%20British%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EF%3C%2Fspan%3EIFPRO%E2%80%99s%20legal%20director%2C%20Roy%20Vermeer%2C%20told%20DW%20that%20Zambia%E2%80%99s%20case%20didn%E2%80%99t%20surprise%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20shocked%20by%20the%20allegations%20obviously%2C%20but%20we%20were%20not%20shocked%20that%20this%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%C2%A0Vermeer%20who%20said%20it%20is%20a%20structural%20problem%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20which%20occurs%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ES%3C%2Fspan%3Eexual%20misconduct%20has%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20Sierre%20Leone%20and%20Gabon%20teams.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20cases%20of%20abuse%20reported%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Venezuela%2C%20Australia%2C%20Haiti%20and%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EFIFPRO%20e%3C%2Fspan%3Explained%20in%20a%20report%20that%20football%20is%20a%20high-risk%20environment%20for%20sexual%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20great%20number%20of%20athletes%C2%A0are%20aiming%20for%20a%20big%20career%2C%20including%20many%20young%20people%20from%20lower%20socio-economic%20backgrounds%20who%20want%C2%A0to%20lift%20themselves%20and%20their%20families%20out%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20gives%20coaches%20and%20administrators%20a%20lot%20of%C2%A0power%2C%20which%20oftentimes%C2%A0comes%20with%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20abuse%20for%20the%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20national%20federations%20there%20is%20often%20no%20interest%20in%20investigating%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Vermeer%20explained%20to%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20federation%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20members%20happy%20who%20vote%20for%20you.%20These%20are%20the%20regional%20association%20and%20clubs%2C%20not%20the%20players.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20needed%2C%20explained%20Vermeer%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eone%20independent%20entity%20for%C2%A0footballers%20that%20investigates%20abuses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20might%20take%20longer%2C%20there%20are%20things%20that%20could%20be%20changed%20right%20away%2C%20%E2%80%9Clike%20a%20gender%20balance%20in%20panels%20that%20hear%20the%20cases%20as%20well%20as%20a%20trauma-informed%20and%20victim-centric%20approach%20in%20federations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20legal%20director%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnfair%20treatments%20still%20in%20place%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoor%20working%20conditions%2C%20unfair%20payments%20and%20sexual%20misconduct%20are%20still%20very%20much%20in%20place%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20teams%20in%20Africa%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20on%20a%20global%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EYe%3C%2Fspan%3Et%2C%20across%20African%20teams%20there%20have%20been%20some%20improvements%2C%20like%20equal%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20gives%20players%20chance%20to%20talk%20about%20unfair%20treatment%20and%20be%20heard%2C%20encouraging%20also%20other%20women%20to%20speak%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20%E2%80%93%20as%20we%20can%20see%20%E2%80%93%20more%20and%20more%20women%20around%20the%20world%C2%A0%20are%20raising%20their%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689747867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19115324%2F2443577055_1547c59793_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fsexism-haunts-african-womens-football-ahead-of-world-cup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20African%20teams%20are%20competing%20in%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%2C%20but%20their%20enthusiasm%20is%20eroded%20by%20poor%20labor%20conditions%2C%20unfair%20payments%20and%20sexual%20abuse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fsexism-haunts-african-womens-football-ahead-of-world-cup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Seeks%20Union%2C%20Kerala%20Govt's%20Response%20Over%20Distribution%20of%20'Poisonous'%20Homeopathic%20Meds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19114055%2F3758019043_c7400b5071_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20July%2018%20sought%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Union%20Ayush%20ministry%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20and%20a%20central%20research%20body%20over%20the%20administration%20of%20a%20certain%20%E2%80%93%20allegedly%20poisonous%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20homeopathic%20medicine%20as%20a%20purported%20COVID-19%20preventive%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fupreme-court-seeks-centres-response-on-plea-challenging-administration-of-homeo-medicine-arsenic-album-30-as-immunity-booster-233011%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20and%20Justice%20S.V.%20Bhatti%20asked%20the%20state%20government%2C%20Union%20ministry%20and%20the%20Central%20Council%20for%20Research%20Homoeopathy%20to%20file%20their%20replies%20in%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Dr%20Cyriac%20Abby%20Philips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyush%20is%20an%20acronym%20that%20stands%20for%20Ayurveda%2C%20Yoga%20and%20Naturopathy%2C%20Unani%2C%20Siddha%2C%20Sowa%20Rigpa%20and%20Homoeopathy.%20This%20ministry%20was%20founded%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20term%20as%20prime%20minister%20and%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayush-ministry-wuhan-coronavirus-ayurveda-homeopathy-unani-clinical-trials%5C%22%3Ecriticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20advocacy%20of%20unproven%20cures.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayush-ministry-wuhan-coronavirus-ayurveda-homeopathy-unani-clinical-trials%5C%22%3Eanalysed%3C%2Fa%3E%20problems%20of%20Ayush%E2%80%99s%20COVID-19%20prevention%20advisories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilips%20has%20challenged%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20medicine%20%E2%80%98Arsenic%20Album%2030%E2%80%99%20to%20children%20and%20elderly%20people%20above%2065%2C%20and%20also%20the%20guidelines%2C%20advisory%20and%20%E2%80%98fact%20sheets%E2%80%99%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Ayush%20permitting%20the%20administration%20of%20homeopathic%20medicine%20in%20various%20situations.%20He%20has%20noted%20in%20the%20plea%20that%20the%20Union%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20guidelines%20meant%20that%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20poisonous%20carcinogens%20like%20arsenic%20became%20part%20of%20the%20homeopathic%20medicine%20prescribed%20by%20some%20of%20state%20governments%20like%20Kerala.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilips%E2%80%99%20plea%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%20to%20mass%20distribute%20Arsenicum%20Album%2030CH%20which%20contains%20%E2%80%9Carsenic%2C%20king%20of%20all%20poisons%2C%20a%20metalloid%20and%20known%20carcinogen%20to%20school%20children%2C%20numbering%20anywhere%20between%2038%20lakh%20to%2050%20lakh%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20shocking.%20Six%20lakh%20such%20medicines%20have%20been%20distributed%20already%2C%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Anand%20Grover%20said%20that%20homeopathic%20medicines%20were%20being%20distributed%20without%20any%20%E2%80%9Cbasis%E2%80%9D%20and%20without%20there%20having%20been%20any%20clinical%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20study%20done%20by%20homeopathic%20experts%20shows%20it%20is%20not%20effective.%20They%20are%20not%20going%20by%20the%20drugs%20and%20cosmetics%20act%2C%20they%20are%20not%20carrying%20out%20clinical%20studies.%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated.%20Grover%20also%20stressed%20that%20the%20Kerala%20government%20also%20needed%20to%20file%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bose%20noted%20that%20he%20also%20%E2%80%9Csometimes%20take%20such%20medicines%E2%80%9D%20but%20observed%20in%20contrary%20to%20the%20Union%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20stand%2C%20that%20Arsenic%20Album%20is%20poisonous%20depending%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Clevel%20of%20dilution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilips%20has%20also%20sought%20to%20refer%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20COVID%20task%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689747319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19114055%2F3758019043_c7400b5071_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fsupreme-court-ayush-ministry-kerala-arsenic-album-covid-homeopathy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Petitioner%20Dr%20Cyriac%20Abby%20Philips%20has%20said%20that%20thanks%20to%20Ayush%20ministry%20guidelines%2C%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20poisonous%20carcinogens%20like%20arsenic%26quot%3B%20are%20part%20of%20homeopathic%20medicines%20which%20are%20being%20distributed%20to%20lakhs%20of%20children%20in%20Kerala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fsupreme-court-ayush-ministry-kerala-arsenic-album-covid-homeopathy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Fiery%20crash%20as%20passenger%20train%20ploughs%20into%20truck%20in%20Indonesia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689747144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F94C1%2Fproduction%2F_130418083_p0g1nm71.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66241233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20person%20is%20injured%20as%20a%20train%20crashes%20into%20a%20broken-down%20truck%20in%20Indonesia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-66241233%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20facing%20'exceptio