2F01%2F11174740%2FDassault_Rafale_M_of_Flottille_17F_lands_aboard_USS_George_H.W._Bush_CVN-77_in_the_Atlantic_Ocean_on_10_May_2018_180510-N-UV609-0540.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EDiscussions%20around%20cost%20and%20techno-commercial%20details%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20purchase%20of%2026%20Rafale-M%20fighter%20jets%20and%20three%20Scorpene%20submarines%20from%20France%20are%20still%20reportedly%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Ftechno-commercial-negotiations-on-rafale-m-scorpene-projects-yet-to-be-firmed-up-sources%2Farticleshow%2F101854329.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20state-run%20ship-builder%20Mazagon%20Dock%20Limited%20(MDL)%20and%20French%20defence%20major%20Naval%20Group%20finalised%20a%20framework%20agreement%20on%20July%206%20for%20the%20Scorpene%20submarine%20project%2C%20but%20conversations%20on%20price%20and%20other%20technical%20details%20have%20not%20yet%20concluded.%20On%20the%20Rafale-M%20procurement%20too%2C%20techno-commercial%20details%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2013%2C%20the%20defence%20acquisition%20council%20(DAC)%20cleared%20the%20Indian%20Navy%E2%80%99s%20proposals%20to%20acquire%2026%20Rafale%20M%20jets%20and%20three%20submarines.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20day%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20began%20his%20two-day%20visit%20to%20France%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20the%20two%20purchases%20would%20be%20announced%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-and-france-yet-to-finalize-deals-for-acquisition-of-rafale-jets-and-scorpene-submarines-negotiations-ongoing-101689668927455.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20two%20deals%20did%20not%20figure%20in%20the%2025-year%20roadmap%20chalked%20out%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20purchases%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20India%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20clear%E2%80%9D%20about%20acquiring%20the%20Rafale%20M%20jets%20and%20Scorpene%20submarines%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issues%20still%20up%20for%20negotiation%20are%20reportedly%20pricing%2C%20date%20of%20delivery%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9CMake%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20component.%20Though%20the%20final%20price%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20decided%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20deal%20will%20cost%20between%20nine%20and%2010%20billion%20euros%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-france-negotiations-scorpene-combat-jet-engine-deals-not-yet-done-missing-from-final-statement-8842700%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20negotiators%20tried%20to%20finish%20talks%20on%20these%20two%20big%20purchases%20while%20Modi%20was%20in%20France%2C%20but%20could%20not%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20negotiators%20tried%20to%20close%20the%20two%20deals%20in%20time%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20include%20the%20lines%20in%20the%20document.%20But%20that%20could%20not%20be%20wrapped%20up%20by%20the%20summit%20meeting%E2%80%A6%20It%20went%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20till%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20French%20President%20met%20and%20discussed%20the%20matter%E2%80%A6%20but%20could%20not%20be%20closed%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20source%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20draft%20version%20of%20the%20final%20joint%20statement%20had%20reportedly%20been%20uploaded%20%E2%80%9Cby%20mistake%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%E2%80%99%20website%2C%20which%20included%20a%20line%20on%20the%20Scorpene%20submarines.%20This%20line%20was%20not%20in%20the%20final%20joint%20statement.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%98Horizon%202047%3A%2025th%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20India-France%20Strategic%20Partnership%2C%20Towards%20A%20Century%20of%20India-France%20Relations%E2%80%99%20now%20states%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20and%20France%20hail%20the%20success%20of%20the%20first%20Scorpene%20submarine%20construction%20programme%20(P75%20%E2%80%93%20Kalvari)%2C%20a%20model%20of%20Make%20in%20India%20and%20the%20sharing%20of%20naval%20expertise%20between%20companies%20in%20the%20two%20countries.%20India%20and%20France%20are%20ready%20to%20explore%20more%20ambitious%20projects%20to%20develop%20the%20Indian%20submarine%20fleet%20and%20its%20performance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20draft%20statement%20uploaded%20by%20%E2%80%9Cmistake%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20was%20also%20a%20sentence%20that%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20welcome%20the%20MoU%20between%20Mazagon%20Dockyard%20Ltd%20and%20Naval%20Group%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20three%20additional%20submarines%20under%20the%20P75%20programme.%E2%80%9D%20This%20line%20is%20not%20there%20in%20the%20final%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689745457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F11174740%2FDassault_Rafale_M_of_Flottille_17F_lands_aboard_USS_George_H.W._Bush_CVN-77_in_the_Atlantic_Ocean_on_10_May_2018_180510-N-UV609-0540.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findias-purchase-of-rafale-scorpene-from-france-not-announced-because-negotiations-still-on%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20issues%20still%20up%20for%20negotiation%20are%20reportedly%20pricing%2C%20date%20of%20delivery%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9CMake%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20component.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findias-purchase-of-ra