20decades%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esystematic%20attempts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20present%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20violence%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eappear%20as%20something%20that%20was%20intentionally%20hyped%20in%20the%20public%20perception%20by%20a%20few%20people%2C%20including%20rights%20activists%20like%20Setalvad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20difference%20now%20is%20that%20this%20narrative%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%20part%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20make%20light%20of%20the%202002%20riots%2C%C2%A0%20is%20now%20being%20presented%20as%20fact%20in%20the%20courts%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20it%20becomes%20important%20to%20recall%20that%20Setalvad%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20%E2%80%9Ctarnishing%E2%80%9D%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20image.%20Independent%20institutions%20like%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20have%20also%20made%20strong%20observations%20in%20the%20past%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20violence%20and%20the%20role%20of%20the%20government%20he%20ran%20as%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-order-teesta-setalvad%5C%22%3ECondemned%20by%20Innuendo%3A%20Some%20Questions%20on%20the%20SC%20Order%20That%20Led%20to%20Teesta%20Setalvad%E2%80%99s%20Arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENational%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20taking%20immediate%20cognisance%20of%20the%20riots%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20NHRC%20in%202002%20not%20only%20asked%20the%20government%20of%20Gujarat%20to%20submit%20a%20report%2C%20but%20also%20visited%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NHRC%20at%20the%20time%20was%20headed%20by%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20J.S.%20Verma.%20Justice%20K.%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Justice%20Sujata%20Manohar%20and%20Virendra%20Dayal%20are%20signatories%20to%20its%20proceedings%E2%80%99%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20proceedings%2C%20the%20commission%C2%A0had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhrc.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fgo.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20%5Blight%5D%20of%20the%20history%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20recalled%20in%20the%20report%20of%20the%20state%20government%20itself%2C%20the%20question%20must%20arise%20whether%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eres%C2%A0ipsa%C2%A0loquitur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98the%20affair%20speaking%20for%20itself%E2%80%99)%20should%20not%20apply%20in%20this%20case%20in%20assessing%20the%20degree%20of%20state%20responsibility%20in%20the%20failure%20to%20protect%20the%20life%2C%20liberty%2C%20equality%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gujarat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20posing%20this%20question%2C%20the%20commission%20gave%20the%20state%20government%20time%20to%20respond%20and%20refute%20the%20common%20perception%20that%20it%20had%20failed%20in%20fulfilling%20its%20responsibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20also%20noted%20the%20discrimination%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20compensation%20awarded%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20which%20it%20said%20led%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20adverse%20comment%20both%20within%20the%20country%20and%20abroad%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20compensation%20to%20the%20next-of-kin%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20riots%20was%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20the%20amount%20offered%20to%20the%20next-of-kin%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Godhra%20train%20incident%20was%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20The%20commission%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20subsequently%20offered%20Rs%201%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20next-of-kin%20in%20all%20instances%20to%20%E2%80%9Cestablish%20parity%E2%80%9D%2C%20although%20after%20supposedly%20receiving%20a%20letter%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20advocating%20this%20approach.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20proceedings%C2%A0on%20May%2031%2C%202002%2C%20after%20receiving%20an%20unsatisfactory%20response%20from%20the%20state%20government%2C%20the%20NHRC%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhrc.nic.in%2Fpress-release%2Ffurther-proceedings-commission-situation-gujarat%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20it%20has%C2%A0reached%20the%20definite%20conclusion%20that%20the%C2%A0principle%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eres%C2%A0ipsa%C2%A0loquitur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20applies%20in%20this%20case%20and%20that%20there%20was%20a%C2%A0%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20failure%20of%C2%A0the%20state%20to%20protect%20the%20constitutional%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20tragedy%20in%C2%A0Godhra%20on%20February%2027%2C%202002%20and%20continuing%20with%20the%20violence%20that%20ensued%20in%20the%20weeks%20that%C2%A0followed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FGodhra-train-PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20coach%20of%20the%20Sabarmati%20Express%20train%20which%20was%20torched.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%2FFiles%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22772%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-185847%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20coach%20of%20the%20Sabarmati%20Express%20train%20which%20was%20torched.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%2FFiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20riots%2C%20the%20ECI%20visited%20the%20state%20to%20gauge%20if%20elections%20could%20be%20conducted%20or%20not.%20In%20its%20report%2C%20it%20stated%20that%20there%20were%20contradictions%20within%20what%20the%20state%20government%20had%20reported%20in%20the%20report%20on%20law%20and%20order%2C%20and%20what%20the%20state%20government%20was%20actually%20doing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20state%20government%20reported%20that%20only%2012%20districts%20were%20affected%2C%20whereas%20the%20scheme%20of%C2%A0distribution%C2%A0of%20free%20rations%20has%20been%20extended%20to%2020%20districts.%C2%A0Regarding%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20omission%2C%20the%20ECI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.pib.gov.in%2Farchive%2Freleases98%2Flyr2002%2Fraug2002%2F16082002%2Fr160820029.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%20as%20follows%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20Government%20%5Bhas%5D%20on%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20queries%20subsequently%20been%20avoiding%20giving%20a%20clear%20picture%20of%20the%20number%20and%20identity%20of%20persons%20complained%20against%2C%20similar%20details%20of%20persons%20included%20in%20the%20FIRs%2C%20similar%20details%20of%20persons%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20similar%20details%20of%20persons%20named%20in%20the%20FIRs%20who%20have%20been%20enlarged%20on%20bail%2C%20%5Band%5D%20similar%20details%20of%20persons%20enlarged%20on%20bail%20as%20against%20whom%20appeals%20have%20been%20filed%20for%20cancellation%20of%20their%20bail%20bonds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommission%20of%20inquiry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20appointed%20the%20Nanavati-Mehta%20Commission%20to%20look%20into%20the%20Godhra%20train%20burning%20incident%20and%20its%20scope%20was%20later%20expanded%20to%20look%20into%20the%20riots%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20over%201%2C000%20deaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nanavati-Mehta%20Commission%20also%20examined%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20administrative%20actions%20taken%20to%20prevent%20these%20incidents%2C%20whether%20the%20Godhra%20incident%20was%20premeditated%20and%20if%20the%20authorities%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20to%20prevent%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%202004%2C%20the%20Commission%20broadened%20its%20investigation%20to%20include%20the%20role%20and%20participation%20of%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20Modi%2C%20his%20ministers%2C%20police%20officers%2C%20and%20other%C2%A0individuals%20and%20organisations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20state%20government%20did%20this%20of%20its%20own%20volition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnanavati-commission-gujarat-2002-violence-bjp-electoral-gains%5C%22%3EGujarat%20Riots%20Spontaneous%20Says%20Nanavati%20Panel%2C%20But%20Electoral%20Data%20Shows%20Method%20in%20Madness%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESupreme%20Court%20of%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20hearing%20a%20petition%20demanding%20the%20retrial%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F105430%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20Bakery%20Case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(which%20involved%20the%20killing%20of%2014%20people%20during%20the%20riots)%2C%20the%20then-Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Justice%20V.N.%20Khare%C2%A0had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fsouth_asia%2F3102864.stm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremarked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20he%20has%C2%A0no%20faith%20left%20in%20the%20prosecution%20and%20the%20Gujarat%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%C2%A0months%20after%20this%20remark%20was%20made%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20a%20retrial%20to%20be%20held%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20top%20court%20directed%20the%20retrial%20while%20%E2%80%9Ckeeping%20in%20view%20the%20peculiar%20circumstances%20of%20the%20case%2C%20and%20the%20ample%20evidence%20on%20record%20glaringly%20demonstrating%20subversion%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20justice%20delivery%20system%20with%20no%20congeal%20and%20conducive%20atmosphere%20still%20prevailing%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20remarked%20that%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20was%20not%20fair%20and%20impartial%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20modern-day%20%E2%80%98Neros%E2%80%99%20were%20looking%20elsewhere%20when%20Best%20Bakery%20and%20innocent%20children%20and%20helpless%20women%20were%C2%A0burning%2C%20and%C2%A0were%20probably%20deliberating%20how%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20crime%20can%20be%20saved%20or%20protected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELaw%20and%20justice%20become%20flies%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20these%20%E2%80%9Cwanton%20boys%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20fences%20start%20to%20swallow%20the%20crops%2C%20no%20scope%20will%20be%20left%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20survival%20of%20law%20and%20order%20or%20truth%20and%20justice.%20Public%20order%20as%20well%20as%20public%20interest%20become%20martyrs%20and%20monuments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20not%20the%20only%20case%20where%20the%20trial%20was%20moved%20out%20of%20Gujarat.%20The%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20also%20directed%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20convicts%20are%20now%20out%20on%20remission%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Findia%2Fbilkis-bano-case-timeline-1503101084.html%5C%22%3Eto%20be%20moved%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20of%20Gujarat%20to%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20these%20three%20institutions%2C%20committees%20like%20the%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20Empowerment%20of%20Women%20also%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20the%C2%A0bounden%C2%A0duty%20of%20every%20state%20machinery%20to%20take%20pre-emptive%C2%A0steps%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20violence.%C2%A0The%20committee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcjp.org.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FAnnexure-C.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eregretted%20to%20note%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20the%20failure%20to%C2%A0anticipate%20the%20potential%20dangers%20of%20the%20situation%20by%C2%A0the%20Intelligence%20services%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%C2%A0violence%2C%20death%20and%20destruction%20of%20the%20magnitude%C2%A0that%20was%20witnessed%20in%20Gujarat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689719544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24173232%2FAhmedabad_riots1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbefore-teesta-eci-sc-and-nhrc-also-tarnished-modis-image%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20independent%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20a%20group%20that%20also%20includes%20the%20Election%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20criticised%20the%20Gujarat%20government's%20role%20in%20the%202002%20riots.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbefore-teesta-eci-sc-and-nhrc-also-tarnished-modis-image%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%209%20House%20Democrats%20voted%20against%20a%20resolution%20declaring%20Israel%20is%20'not%20a%20racist%20or%20apartheid%20state'%22%2C%22content%