20being%20held%20as%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20scope%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20NDA%20has%20increased%2C%20and%20to%20pursue%20the%20development%20agenda%2C%20and%20to%20meet%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Indian%20polity%2C%20political%20parties%20across%20the%20country%20have%20committed%20themselves%20to%20the%20development%20agenda%20which%20is%20why%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20has%20also%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Our%2038%20partners%20have%20confirmed%20attending%20the%20NDA%20meeting%20to%20be%20held%20tomorrow%2C%20says%20BJP%20National%20President%20JP%20Nadda.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FDFNip4inNA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FDFNip4inNA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1680911419997585408%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20NDA%20partners%2C%20too%2C%20are%20upbeat%20about%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20list%20released%20by%20Doordarshan%2C%20the%20parties%20that%20will%20attend%20the%20meeting%20include%20Shiv%20Sena%20(the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction)%2C%20and%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(the%20one%20led%20by%20Pashupati%20Kumar%20Paras).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20parties%20include%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%2C%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20National%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%2C%20Nationalist%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20(NDPP)%2C%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%2C%20Sikkim%20Krantikari%20Morcha%2C%20Mizo%20National%20Front%2C%20Indigenous%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20of%20Tripura%2C%20Naga%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(Nagaland)%2C%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(Athawale)%2C%20Asom%20Gana%20Parishad%2C%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%2C%20Tamil%20Maanila%20Congress%2C%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20Liberal%2C%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20others%20are%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(Sanyukt)%2C%20Maharashtrawadi%20Gomantak%20Party%2C%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%2C%20Prahar%20Janshakti%20Party%2C%20Rashtriya%20Samaj%20Paksha%2C%20Jan%20Surajya%20Shakti%20Party%2C%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%2C%20United%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20Nishad%20Party%2C%20All%20India%20N.R.%20Congress%2C%20Hindustan%20Awami%20Morcha%2C%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%2C%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%2C%20Bharath%20Dharma%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20Kerala%20Kamaraj%20Congress%2C%20Puthiya%20Tamilagam%2C%20Lok%20Jan%20Shakti%20Party%20and%20Gorkha%20National%20Liberation%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%2038%20parties%2C%20that%20will%20attend%20meeting%20the%20NDA%20meeting%20today%20are%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAv6QNVo2WA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAv6QNVo2WA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20DD%20News%20(%40DDNewslive)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDDNewslive%2Fstatus%2F1681215311431839745%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20meeting%20comes%20even%20as%20the%20opposition%20parties%20unite%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20finalise%20plans%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20united%20fight%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20installment%20of%20the%20opposition%20party%20meeting%20has%20also%20seen%20the%20number%20of%20parties%20rising%20from%2017%20in%20Patna%20last%20month%20to%2026%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20call%20the%20NDA%20meeting%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20opposition%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20NDA.%20We%20have%20had%20several%20meetings%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20besides%2C%20this%20is%20also%20the%20silver%20jubilee%20year%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%E2%80%9D%20Syed%20Zafar%20Islam%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%202024%20elections%20are%20near%20and%20all%20parties%20have%20different%20issues%20and%20agendas%2C%20so%20we%20will%20be%20discussing%20that%20along%20with%20the%20evolving%20political%20issues%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20meeting%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-opposition-parties-meet-in-bengaluru-here-are-the-9-big-factors-at-play%5C%22%3E%20focused%20on%20finding%20a%20name%20for%20the%20alliance%20and%20setting%20a%20common%20minimum%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20around%20%E2%80%9Csafeguarding%20democracy%2C%20constitution%2C%20and%20secularism%E2%80%9D%20and%20livelihood%20issues%20like%20inflation%20and%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20NDA%20meeting%2C%20which%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20top%20leaders%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20and%20ways%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdiscuss%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20giving%20specific%20details%20on%20whether%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20will%20be%20discussed%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20that%20such%20talks%20will%20come%20at%20a%20later%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20(seat-sharing%20talks)%20usually%20happens%20at%20a%20later%20stage.%20At%20present%2C%20evolving%20political%20issues%20will%20be%20discussed.%20Every%20party%20has%20its%20own%20agenda%20and%20issues%2C%20so%20all%20important%20issues%20will%20have%20to%20be%20discussed%20and%20deliberated%20upon%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20BJP%20trying%20to%20bring%20regional%20players%20on%20board%20in%20the%20recent%20weeks%20after%20losing%20traditional%20allies%20such%20as%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%2C%20however%2C%20been%20successful%20in%20making%20alliances%20with%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fec-recognises-shinde-faction-as-real-shiv-sena-allots-bow-and-arrow-symbol%5C%22%3EEknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20recognised%20as%20the%20real%20party%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fajit-pawar-rebellion-opposition-unity%5C%22%3Efaction%20of%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar-led%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20(SBSP)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-om-prakash-rajbhars-return-to-nda-mean-for-up-politics%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20Upendra%20Kushwala-led%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Samta%20Party%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi-led%20Hindustani%20Awami%20Morcha%20have%20also%20returned%20to%20the%20alliance%20after%20leaving%20the%20NDA%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20ally%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20however%2C%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20said%20that%20whether%20former%20alliance%20partners%20want%20to%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20or%20not%20is%20up%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20maintain%20our%20coalition%20dharma%20and%20we%20have%20never%20asked%20anyone%20to%20leave.%20If%20anyone%20has%20left%20and%20wants%20to%20come%20back%20we%20always%20welcome%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjobs-justice-and-smart-cities-the-promises-bjp-made-in-its-2014-manifesto%5C%22%3EJobs%2C%20Justice%20and%20Smart%20Cities%3A%20The%20Promises%20BJP%20Made%20in%20Its%202014%20Manifesto%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20agenda%20of%20the%20meeting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslam%20added%20that%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20meeting%20will%20be%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccentrifugal%20force%20which%20is%20our%20common%20ideology%2C%20i.e.%20the%20governance%20model%20which%20focusses%20on%20protecting%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20empowered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20have%20remained%20the%20objectives%20of%20our%20government%20and%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20deliver%20them%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Today%20the%20common%20man%20is%20feeling%20empowered%20while%20India%20has%20also%20become%20an%20important%20global%20player%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20himself%20is%20a%20powerful%20global%20leader%20now.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20common%20man%20as%20well%20as%20among%20our%20alliance%20partners.%20We%20have%20accomplished%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20in%20these%20nine%20years%2C%20which%20we%20had%20promised%20in%202014%2C%20and%20we%20will%20highlight%20this%20and%20discuss%20all%20important%20issues%20for%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20meeting%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20he%20(PM%20Modi)%20is%20stronger%20than%20the%20entire%20opposition%20and%20he%20alone%20is%20enough%20for%20them%2C%20why%20is%20he%20calling%20together%2030%20parties%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20asked%20while%20speaking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1680822519501299713%5C%22%3E%C2%A0to%20ANI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C..They%20are%20baffled%20by%20what%20we%20are%20doing%2C%20so%20they%20are%20gathering%20factions%20of%20parties%20to%20show%20their%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20meeting%20has%2C%20however%2C%20also%20caught%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20virtual%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Veer%20Savarkar%20International%20Airport%20in%20Port%20Blair%2C%20Modi%20called%20the%20ongoing%20opposition%20meeting%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EKattar%20Bhrashtachar%20Sammelan%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20(hardcore%20corruption%20convention).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20have%20already%20decided%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%202024%20and%20those%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1681180676798959616%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20plight%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20India%20have%20set%20up%20their%20own%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20of%20the%20country%20say%20that%20this%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Kattar%20Bhrashtachar%20Sammelan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6Another%20specialty%20of%20this%20meeting%20is%20that%20if%20someone%20is%20out%20on%20bail%20in%20a%20corruption%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20they%20are%20seen%20with%20great%20respect.%20If%20the%20entire%20family%20is%20