%20But%20things%20changed%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKauther%20says%20her%20decision%20to%20leave%20ABVP%20provoked%20abuses%20and%20threats%20from%20her%20former%20friends%20in%20the%20group.%20She%20eventually%20became%20friends%20with%20the%20same%20Muslim%20student%20activists%20whom%20she%20had%20called%20%E2%80%9Cextremists%E2%80%9D%20when%20she%20was%20a%20part%20of%20ABVP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20fear%20of%20repercussion%2C%20Kauther%20did%20not%20get%20her%20conversion%20notified%20officially%20in%20the%20government%20gazette.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20need%20to%20sign%20an%20affidavit%2C%20submit%20documents%2C%20and%20advertise%20the%20change%20of%20religion%20in%20the%20papers%20if%20I%20want%20to%20convert%20officially.%20My%20family%20will%20surely%20come%20to%20know%20of%20my%20decision%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20if%20not%20my%20parents%2C%20my%20relatives%20will%20definitely%20retaliate%20violently%20as%20it%20becomes%20an%20issue%20of%20so-called%20honour%20of%20the%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECases%20of%20social%20ostracisation%2C%20torture%2C%20and%20attacks%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20on%20mere%20suspicion%20of%20conversion%20to%20minority%20religions%20have%20been%20widely%20reported%20of%20late.%20Kauther%20thus%20fears%20that%20she%20might%20be%20made%20an%20example%20of%2C%20given%20the%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20in%20a%20large%20way%2C%20contributed%20to%20Kauther%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20her%20studies.%20She%20adds%20that%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20say%20where%20she%20lives%20out%20of%20continuing%20fear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKauther%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20not%20an%20aberration.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20people%20who%20act%20as%20spies%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations%20at%20places%20like%20affidavit%20shops%2C%20notary%20services%20and%20even%20government%20offices.%20So%2C%20whenever%20somebody%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20religion%20change%20registration%2C%20the%20organisations%20like%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20hound%20them.%20They%20also%20inform%20and%20pressurise%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramees%20E.K.%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Student%20Islamic%20Organization%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-639193%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EState%20%E2%80%98interference%E2%80%99%20and%20persecution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20downslide%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20religious%20freedom%2C%20has%20been%20a%20topic%20both%20globally%20and%20nationally.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20topic%20of%20the%20only%20question%20taken%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20during%20his%20recent%20US%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20US%20Commission%20for%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%2C%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20flagged%20India%20for%20%E2%80%9Cseverely%20deteriorating%E2%80%9D%20religious%20freedoms.%20It%20has%20designated%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98country%20of%20particular%20concern%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20right%20to%20convert%20to%20any%20other%20religion%20is%20safeguarded%20in%20Article%2025%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20ensures%20that%20all%20individuals%20are%20equally%20entitled%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%20of%20conscience%20and%20the%20right%20freely%20to%20profess%2C%20practise%20and%20propagate%20their%20religion%E2%80%9D.%20But%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20overlooking%20the%20constitutional%20rights%20and%20introducing%20new%20laws%20in%20their%20ruling%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccriminalise%E2%80%9D%20conversion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20today%2C%20ten%20Indian%20states%2C%20most%20of%20them%20ruled%20by%20BJP%20have%20sanctioned%20anti-conversion%20laws%20which%20are%20popularised%20as%20%E2%80%9Clove%20jihad%E2%80%9D%20laws%2C%20giving%20credence%20to%20the%20bogey%20that%20there%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20afoot%20through%20which%20Muslim%20men%20convert%20Hindu%20women%20through%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20with%20talk%20on%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20mostly%20targeting%20Muslims%2C%20critics%20say%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20been%20enacting%20discriminatory%20legislation%20in%20states%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%9Canti-conversion%20laws.%E2%80%9D%20For%20instance%20in%20Uttarakhand%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%C2%A0%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Freedom%20of%20Religion%20Act%20was%20enacted%20in%202018%20with%20the%20stated%20objective%20%E2%80%9Cto%20provide%20freedom%20of%20religion%20by%20the%20prohibition%20of%20conversion%20from%20one%20religion%20to%20another%20by%20misrepresentation%2C%20force%2C%20undue%20influence%2C%20coercion%2C%20allurement%20or%20by%20any%20fraudulent%20means%20or%20by%20marriage%20and%20for%20the%20matters%20incidental%20thereto%E2%80%9D.%20But%20according%20to%20the%20law%2C%20if%20any%20person%20returns%20to%20their%20%E2%80%9Cancestral%20religion%E2%80%9D%2C%20such%20an%20act%20shall%20not%20be%20deemed%20conversion%20under%20the%20Act.%20This%20essentially%20means%20conversion%20to%20Hinduism%20from%20any%20other%20religion%20is%20largely%20spared%20from%20investigation%20under%20this%20law.%20Hindu%20supremacist%20groups%20like%20RSS%20argue%20that%20all%20Indians%20are%20originally%20Hindus%20irrespective%20of%20the%20religion%20they%20follow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Flies-insistence-and-disregard-for-evidence-the-journey-of-love-jihad-laws%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520spate%2520of%2520legislation%2520surrounding%2Cevidence%2520to%2520support%2520these%2520claims%253F%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520myth%2520of%2520%2527love%2520jihad%2Cto%2520rest%252C%2520rises%2520yet%2520again.%5C%22%3ELies%2C%20Insistence%20and%20Disregard%20for%20Evidence%3A%20The%20Journey%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Laws%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20anti-conversion%20laws%20not%20only%20criminalise%20personal%20choices%20of%20choosing%20one%E2%80%99s%20religion%20%E2%80%93%20specifically%20if%20that%20religion%20happens%20to%20be%20either%20Islam%20or%20Christianity%20%E2%80%93%20but%20more%20worryingly%20targets%20religious%20leaders%20of%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr.%20Mohammad%20Reyaz%2C%20an%20academic%20who%20works%20on%20issues%20of%20minority%20marginalisation.%20%E2%80%9CSimply%20put%2C%20the%20so-called%20anti-conversion%20laws%20are%20always%20one-step%20closer%20to%20making%20India%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20%5BHindu%20nation%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20laws%20are%20only%20applied%20if%20Hindus%20convert%20to%20Islam%20or%20Christianity.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Muslims%20or%20Christians%20converting%20to%20Hinduism%20are%20celebrated%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewapsi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bhomecoming%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23164055%2F2EC978D3-90C7-460D-AE0F-2F02A3393076.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23164055%2F2EC978D3-90C7-460D-AE0F-2F02A3393076.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23164055%2F2EC978D3-90C7-460D-AE0F-2F02A3393076-300x169.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23164055%2F2EC978D3-90C7-460D-AE0F-2F02A3393076-1024x576.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOf%20violence%2C%20death%20and%20destruction%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHailing%20from%20Sitamarhi%20district%20of%20Bihar%2C%2025-year-old%20Pinky%20had%20never%20thought%20that%20the%20new%20faith%20she%20had%20embraced%20would%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20attacks%20on%20her%20and%20her%20husband.%20Born%20in%20a%20Hindu%20family%2C%20Pinky%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20and%20married%20Ram%20Nivas%2C%20a%20pastor%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20from%20Hinduism.%20Their%20conversion%20and%20marriage%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20well%20with%20local%20unit%20of%20VHP.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20local%20VHP%20leaders%20used%20to%20harass%20us.%20They%20never%20let%20us%20live%20peacefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pinky%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0One%20day%20when%20they%20were%20conducting%20a%20prayer%20meeting%20at%20their%20home%2C%20a%20mob%20broke%20into%20their%20house%2C%20destroying%20whatever%20they%20saw%20and%20severely%20thrashing%20Pinky%20and%20Ram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20sustained%20serious%20injuries%2C%20contracted%20COVID-19%20while%20undergoing%20treatment%20and%20died%20within%20days%20of%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20our%20fault%3F%20Can%E2%80%99t%20we%20practice%20our%20faith%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Pinky.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20report%20compiled%20by%20the%20United%20Christian%20Forum%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20organisation%2C%20that%20documented%20cases%20of%20religiously%20motivated%20violence%20against%20Christians%20in%20the%20country%20suggested%20that%202022%20was%20the%20most%20violent%20year%20for%20the%20community.%20The%20country%20witnessed%20522%20cases%20of%20violent%20attacks%20on%20Christians%2C%20the%20highest%20ever%20since%20the%20UCF%20started%20documenting%20such%20attacks%20in%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20almost%20all%20incidents%20reported%20across%20India%2C%20vigilante%20mobs%20comprising%20religious%20extremists%20have%20been%20seen%20to%20either%20barge%20into%20a%20prayer%20gathering%20or%20round%20up%20individuals%20that%20they%20believe%20are%20involved%20in%20forcible%20religious%20conversions.%20With%20impunity%2C%20such%20mobs%20criminally%20threaten%20and%2For%20physically%20assault%20people%20in%20prayer%20before%20handing%20them%20over%20to%20the%20police%20on%20allegations%20of%20forcible%20conversions%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20by%20UCF%20notes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Freligious-conversion-a-serious-issue-shouldnt-be-given-political-colour-says-sc%5C%22%3EReligious%20Conversion%20a%20Serious%20Issue%2C%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20Be%20Given%20%E2%80%98Political%20Colour%E2%80%99%2C%20Says%20SC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThis%20violence%20against%20the%20Christian%20community%20is%20compounded%20by%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20police%20to%20investigate%20and%20prosecute%20mobs%20and%20perpetrators%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAC%20Michael%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Minorities%20Commission%20and%20the%20current%20convenor%20of%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20our%20experience%20of%20handling%20such%20incidents%2C%20we%20can%20easily%20say%20that%20in%20almost%20all%20cases%2C%20the%20police%20and%20the%20local%20authorities%20are%20always%20found%20taking%20sides%20with%20perpetrators.%20In%20fact%2C%20sometimes%2C%20police%20seem%20to%20be%20working%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20perpetrators.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20times%2C%20police%20accompany%20these%20mobs%20who%20attack%20the%20peacefully%20praying%20community%20and%20beat%20up%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children.%20They%20desecrate%20religious%20articles%20and%20burn%20Holy%20Bibles%20under%20the%20watch%20of%20police.%20Government%20has%20never%20taken%20our%20request%20to%20look%20into%20such%20incidents%20seriously%20nor%20have%20they%20taken%20any%20action%20against%20perpetrators%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpen%20Doors%2C%20a%20global%20Christian%20organisation%20that%20tracks%20violence%20against%20the%20community%20across%20the%20world%2C%C2%A0%20ranks%20India%20as%20the%2010th%20most%20dangerous%20country%20for%20Christians.%20For%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20the%20country%20has%20retained%20the%20same%20position.%20The%20watchdog%20in%20its%202022%20report%20mentions%20that%20the%20persecution%20of%20Christians%20in%20India%20is%20intensifying%20as%20Hindu%20extremists%20%E2%80%9Caim%20to%20cleanse%20the%20country%20of%20their%20presence%20and%20influence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20driving%20force%20behind%20this%20is%20Hindutva%2C%20an%20ideology%20that%20disregards%20Indian%20Christians%20and%20other%20religious%20minorities%20as%20true%20Indians%20because%20they%20have%20allegiances%20that%20lie%20outside%20India%20and%20asserts%20the%20country%20should%20be%20purified%20of%20their%20presence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-623441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202017%2C%20RSS%20cadres%20in%20Malappuram%2C%20a%20Muslim-majority%20district%20in%20Kerala%2C%20killed%20Faisal%20P.%20who%20had%20recently%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20Faisal%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20who%20converted%20to%20Islam%20soon%20after%20her%20son%20was%20killed%20and%20assumed%20the%20name%20Jameela%2C%20says%20the%20murder%20was%20intended%20to%20threaten%20Muslims%20into%20submission.%20%E2%80%9DHe%20was%20killed%20only%20because%20he%20embraced%20Islam.%20Even%20our%20relatives%20were%20part%20of%20the%20killing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0When%20Jameela%20and%2016%20members%20of%20her%20family%20converted%20to%20Islam%20after%20Faisal%E2%80%99s%20murder%2C%20they%20were%20also%20threatened%20with%20the%20same%20fate%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKauther%2C%20quoted%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20piece%2C%20had%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20you%20are%20a%20woman%2C%20vulnerabilities%20are%20high%2C%20even%20in%20personal%20circles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%202020%2C%20when%20the%20first%20case%20under%20the%20then%20new%20%E2%80%9Canti-conversion%20law%E2%80%9D%20was%20reported%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Kauther%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%2C%20she%20could%20not%20sleep%20for%20days.%20By%20then%20she%20had%20begun%20learning%20how%20to%20perform%20the%20Islamic%20prayer%20but%20was%20afraid%20to%20do%20so%20in%20public%20or%20at%20home.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%20a%20dozen%20people%20interviewed%20for%20this%20article%2C%20which%20includes%20converts%2C%20activists%2C%20community%20leaders%20and%20legal%20experts%2C%20all%20said%20that%20Hindutva%20groups%20target%20Hindus%20who%20convert%20to%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%20with%20%E2%80%9Cstate%20impunity%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20no%20longer%20feel%20assured%20that%20even%20courts%20would%20protect%20our%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aditya%20Menon%2C%20a%20prominent%20journalist%20based%20out%20of%20India%2C%20who%20converted%20to%20Islam%20as%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20his%20teenage%20years%2C%20Menon%20says%20he%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20a%20strong%20moral%20anchor%2C%20which%20he%20gradually%20began%20to%20find%20in%20Islam.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20praying%20and%20fasting%20much%20later%2C%20only%20when%20I%20was%2021%20and%20had%20moved%20out%20for%20my%20studies%2C%20because%20since%20I%20was%20staying%20with%20family%2C%20I%20could%20not%20do%20it%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMenon%20formalised%20his%20conversion%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20came%20into%20power%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20it%20immediately%20after%20this%20government%20came%20to%20power%20since%20I%20was%20sort%20of%20sure%20that%20they%20would%20introduce%20discriminatory%20laws%20against%20conversions%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Menon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMenon%20says%20that%20his%20identity%20as%20a%20Muslim%20now%20affects%20the%20networking%20that%20is%20required%20in%20his%20profession%2C%20but%20that%20is%20something%20he%20has%20learned%20to%20deal%20with.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20one%20does%20find%20people%20who%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Suffocating%E2%80%99%20atmosphere%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feared%20for%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20M%2C%20a%20journalist%20who%20left%20India%20and%20settled%20in%20Europe%20in%202021%20after%20secretly%20converting%20to%20Islam.%20M%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20reveal%20her%20full%20name%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20harmed.%20She%20says%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20opening%20up%20about%20her%20faith%20to%20her%20parents%20or%20close%20family%20members%20has%20not%20occurred%20to%20her%20even%20once.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Futtarakhand-hate-speech-jihad-anti-muslim%5C%22%3ECross%20Marks%20on%20Doors%2C%20Cries%20of%20Extermination%3A%20How%20Uttarakhand%20Became%20Our%20Hate%20Speech%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20kill%20me%20or%20they%20can%20resort%20to%20rape%20to%20%E2%80%98discipline%E2%80%99%20me.%20This%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%E2%80%9D%20M%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20no%20longer%20associates%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Chome%E2%80%9D%20with%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20continue%20working%20safely%2C%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20seemed%20to%20leave%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20in%20a%20Brahmin%20family%20in%20a%20village%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20M%20says%20Islamophobia%20around%20her%20was%20ubiquitous.%20She%20often%20heard%20her%20family%20members%20blaming%20the%20Muslim%20community%20for%20every%20problem%20in%20the%20country%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%9Charbouring%20callous%20stereotypes%E2%80%9D%20against%20them.%20Things%20became%20worse%20when%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20in%20her%20teens.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20realised%20how%20deep%20their%20hatred%20ran.%20My%20father%20told%20me%20that%20he%20is%20going%20to%20run%20this%20guy%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20M%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0At%20home%2C%20various%20forms%20of%20restrictions%20and%20abuse%20surrounded%20M.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20all%20directed%20at%20regulating%20my%20body%20and%20my%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F15092209%2FScreenshot-2022-02-15-at-9.22.03-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221096%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F15092209%2FScreenshot-2022-02-15-at-9.22.03-AM.png%201096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F15092209%2FScreenshot-2022-02-15-at-9.22.03-AM-300x132.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F15092209%2FScreenshot-2022-02-15-at-9.22.03-AM-1024x449.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-581646%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22481%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20M%20joined%20college%20far%20away%20from%20her%20home%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20radical%20literary%20and%20political%20ideas%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CI%20developed%20a%20naive%20feminist%20rebellion%20as%20well%20as%20anti-caste%20consciousness%2C%20both%20compelling%20forces%20which%20pushed%20me%20out%20of%20my%20familial%20religion.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20I%20got%20introduced%20to%20Islam%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20years%20that%20M%20embraced%20Islam%20and%20began%20to%20practice%20her%20faith%20earnestly.%20However%2C%20considering%20the%20hostile%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20country%2C%20she%20never%20revealed%20her%20new%20religious%20identity%20to%20anyone%2C%20except%20her%20close%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20hide%20my%20faith%20from%20not%20just%20my%20family%20members%2C%20but%20my%20colleagues%20at%20my%20former%20workplace%20as%20well.%20My%20hijab%20was%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Chelmet%E2%80%9D%20by%20one%20of%20my%20bosses%20and%20my%20co-workers%20would%20spread%20rumours%20and%20pass%20crass%20anti-Muslim%20jokes%2C%E2%80%9D%20M%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKauther%20concurs.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20can%20be%20really%20suffocating%20to%20not%20practice%20what%20you%20believe%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20most%2C%20leaving%20the%20country%20like%20Kauther%20or%20M%20is%20not%20even%20remotely%20an%20option.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20would%20we%20go%3F%C2%A0%20We%20are%20being%20harassed%20each%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roshan%2C%20a%20Christian%20convert%20from%20Azamgarh%20city%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%2031%2C%202021%2C%20Roshan%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20attacked%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20who%20accused%20their%20family%20of%20forcefully%20converting%20people%20to%20Christianity.%20His%20father%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%20by%20the%20mob%20where%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20complaint.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20released%20by%20the%20high%20court%20on%20bail%20after%20six%20months.%20He%20was%20jailed%20for%20no%20reason%20and%20had%20to%20endure%20so%20much%20stigma%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roshan%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20were%20afraid%20to%20support%20them%20because%20of%20threats%20from%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%2019-year-old%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Gupta%20was%20among%20three%20men%20who%20were%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwocircles.net%2F2023jan18%2F448029.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20under%20the%20anti-conversion%20law%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Prayagraj%20for%20distributing%20Islamic%20books%20and%20pamphlets%20during%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20festival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20in%20Maloni%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Gupta%20was%20inspired%20by%20his%20uncle%20in%20Fatehpur%2C%20who%20had%20himself%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20atmosphere%20at%20their%20home%20was%20so%20good%20and%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20like%20staying%20there%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20parents%20sensed%20his%20inclination%20towards%20Islam%20and%20refused%20to%20send%20him%20back%20to%20his%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20home.%20%E2%80%9COne%20day%20I%20was%20watching%20a%20movie%20in%20which%20a%20character%20was%20praying.%20Out%20of%20nowhere%20I%20too%20prostrated%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%2C%20who%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20March%2C%20says%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20talk%20around%20it%2C%20it%20is%20still%20not%20a%20crime%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20of%20a%20religion.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F24172919%2FIMG_3148.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22socialist%20future%20socialism%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F24172919%2FIMG_3148.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F24172919%2FIMG_3148-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F24172919%2FIMG_3148-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Proud%20of%20our%20work%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20organisations%20like%20RSS%2C%20VHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20have%20long%20claimed%20that%20Hindus%20in%20the%20country%20are%20being%20forcibly%20converted%20by%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20and%20brought%20to%20their%20%E2%80%98folds%E2%80%99.%20They%20accuse%20Christian%20missionaries%20of%20luring%20poor%20Hindus%20by%20offering%20them%20monetary%20benefits.%20They%20also%20charge%20Muslims%20of%20not%20just%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20explained%20above%20%E2%80%93%20but%20also%20various%20forms%20of%20jihad%2C%20none%20of%20which%20are%20borne%20out%20by%20reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20talked%20to%20several%20members%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations%20who%20stated%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cproud%E2%80%9D%20of%20having%20forcefully%20stopped%20interfaith%20marriages%20and%20religious%20conversations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20can%20never%20be%20love%20between%20a%20Hindu%20girl%20and%20a%20Muslim%20boy.%20No%20such%20love%20exists.%20The%20only%20motive%20is%20of%20converting%20the%20girl%20to%20Islam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yuvraj%20Dwivedi%2C%20the%20District%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Kanpur%20East%20Zone%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5BMuslims%5D%20slaughter%20goats%20and%20chicken.%20Our%20sisters%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20see%20that%20barbarity.%20How%20can%20they%20love%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Dwivedi%20who%20boasts%20about%20having%20%E2%80%9Cstopped%20several%20conversions.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDwivedi%20wants%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20to%20criminalise%20conversion%20from%20Hinduism%20to%20any%20other%20religion.%20%E2%80%9CVHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20are%20standing%20along%20with%20our%20sisters%20and%20protecting%20them.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20demanding%20that%20the%20government%20should%20make%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20laws%20harsher%20and%20take%20action%20to%20prevent%20any%20such%20instances%20from%20happening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDwivedi%20openly%20says%20that%20they%20have%20been%20receiving%20government%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20from%20the%20police%20has%20always%20been%20good.%20There%20is%20never%20any%20situation%20where%20the%20administration%20has%20not%20helped%20us.%20Because%20we%20are%20doing%20the%20right%20job.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERuby%20Dwivedi%2C%20a%20regional%20leader%20of%20Durga%20Vahini%2C%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20wing%20of%20the%20VHP%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20emphasises%20that%20their%20organisation%20can%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20stop%20Hindu%20girls%20from%20%E2%80%9Cfalling%20prey%E2%80%9D%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%20we%20try%20to%20make%20them%20understand%20calmly%20because%20we%20are%20Hindu%20and%20peaceful.%20We%20are%20always%20into%20kindness.%20But%20we%20know%20other%20methods%20and%20systems%20of%20dealing%20with%20them%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20add.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERuby%20also%20said%20that%20Durga%20Vahini%20and%20VHP%20are%20providing%20%E2%80%9Carmy%20like%E2%80%9D%20training%20to%20Hindu%20girls%20to%20save%20them%20from%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20train%20them%20in%20judo%2C%20karate%2C%20sword%20fighting%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20that%20are%20usually%20required%20for%20army%20men%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20protect%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ruby.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20area%2C%20we%20have%20trained%205000-6000%20people.%20We%20organise%20regular%20camps%20in%20every%20district.%20We%20work%20daily%20to%20organise%20camps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-561551%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%20worry%20about%20the%20impunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20strong%20reasons%20to%20be%20afraid%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20John%20Dayal%2C%20human%20rights%20activist.%20Dayal%20is%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20All%20India%20Christian%20Council%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group%20for%20Christians%2C%20who%20make%20up%20roughly%203%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDayal%20believes%20that%20the%20government%20has%20given%20a%20free%20pass%20to%20militant%20Hindutva%20organisations%20to%20harass%20minorities.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20Dayal%20also%20filed%20an%20impleadment%20application%20in%20the%20writ%20petition%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Upadhyaya%20who%20filed%20a%20petition%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20halt%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversions%E2%80%9D%20of%20Hindus%20to%20other%20religions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20itself%20dismissed%20three%20similar%20pleas%20on%20%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversions%E2%80%9D%20filed%20by%20the%20same%20petitioner.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20forced%20conversion.%20Hindus%20are%20the%20majority.%20They%20are%20ruling%20the%20country.%20More%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%20police%20force%20are%20Hindus.%20Almost%20all%20states%20are%20ruled%20by%20Hindus%2C%20with%20some%20exceptions.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20absurd%20to%20say%20there%20is%20mass%20forced%20conversion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dayal%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%20cite%20population%20figures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPercentage%20of%20minority%20population%20in%20India%20has%20either%20remained%20same%20or%20increased%20marginally%20since%20the%20independence%20of%20country%20seven%20decades%20back.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Christians%20was%202%25%20of%20the%20total.%20It%20still%20hovers%20around%20the%20same.%20So%20where%20have%20all%20those%20people%20who%20have%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20gone%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20AC%20Michael.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHanan%20Zaffar%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20filmmaker%20based%20in%20India.%20Shaheen%20Abdulla%20is%20a%20multimedia%20journalist%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20reports%20on%20Indian%20minorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20story%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20Human%20Rights%20and%20Religious%20Freedom%20Journalism%20(HRRFJ)%20grant%20programme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689683418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18112019%2FFEE464CC-1368-48CB-AF2D-1EA659E84547.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20mere%20suspicion%20is%20enough%20to%20unleash%20violence%20and%20threats%20from%20Hindutva%20groups%20or%20police%20action%2C%20those%20who%20have%20converted%20to%20Islam%20or%20Christianity%20believe%20it%20safer%20to%20keep%20their%20faith%20a%20secret.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20state%20troopers%20'told%20to%20push%20migrants%20back%20into%20river%20and%20deny%20them%20water'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%