in%20food.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20knew%20that%20I%20would%20build%20a%20career%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20keep%20the%20legacy%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive%2C%20she%20set%20up%20Manzilat%E2%80%99s%20home%20diner%20in%20Kasba%20of%20Kolkata%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20nawabs%20were%20very%20fond%20of%20food%20and%20Awadhi%20cuisine%20is%20very%20popular%20but%20not%20so%20popular%20outside%20Lucknow.%20People%20even%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20Metiabruz%20do%20not%20know%20the%20history%20associated%20with%20the%20food.%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20towards%20carrying%20the%20legacy%20of%20my%20family%20before%20the%20world%20forgets%20our%20lineage%2